Package userInterface

Class Summary
BusboyUI The BusboyUI class displays the busboy window which shows the map of the tables for the restaurant and their respective status.
ChefUI The ChefUI class displays the window for a chef.
HostUI The HostUI class displays the host window which displays all of the tables in the restaurant and their respective status based on a color-coded system.
LoginUI The LoginUI class displays the login window which shows up at every terminal when no one is logged in to that terminal.
ManagerUI The ManagerUI class displays the window for a manager.
WaiterUI The WaiterUI class displays the window for a waiter.
